headline: 4 Industrial Stocks Poised to Continue Their Winning Streak in 2025
summary: Despite weakness in the manufacturing sector, recovery in the demand environment, with an improvement in the supply chain, augurs well for the industrial sector heading into 2025. ZBRA, RBC, AIT and POWL are likely to continue their momentum.
